01:19:16,079 --> 01:19:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne brinem što mislite.

139
01:19:18,239 --> 01:19:18,960
[SPEAKER_01] To je beznačajno.

140
01:19:19,520 --> 01:19:21,119
[SPEAKER_01] To je samo igra koju um igra.

141
01:19:22,159 --> 01:19:22,960
[SPEAKER_01] Što osjećate?

142
01:19:23,439 --> 01:19:25,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je ono s čime možemo raditi.

143
01:19:25,439 --> 01:19:28,159
[SPEAKER_01] Kemikalije u tijelu, primjećivanje pojava.

144
01:19:29,199 --> 01:19:31,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je osjećaj da se otpustimo, što slijedi?

145
01:19:32,880 --> 01:19:38,800
[SPEAKER_01] Nemojte pokušati razumjeti, nemojte pokušati analizirati, nemojte pokušati shvatiti zašto, kada, što.?

146
01:19:39,760 --> 01:19:41,279
[SPEAKER_01] Beznačajno.

147
01:19:41,840 --> 01:19:42,880
[SPEAKER_01] Što osjećate sada?

148
01:19:45,520 --> 01:19:59,279
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, što mislite o meditaciji ili vizualizaciji ili takvim praksama ili molitvi?

149
01:19:59,920 --> 01:20:01,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ne mislim na ništa od toga.

150
01:20:02,560 --> 01:20:03,920
[SPEAKER_01] Meditacija mi se čini vrijednom.

151
01:20:04,079 --> 01:20:07,920
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno, to povremeno radimo tijekom naših osobnih radionica za čišćenje.

152
01:20:08,800 --> 01:20:16,640
[SPEAKER_01] Lijepo je malo riješiti stvari i, znate, ovisi o pojedincu koliko tiho može uspostaviti um.

153
01:25:58,800 --> 01:26:03,920
[SPEAKER_01] Samo notice da je to bilo tko si bio u to vrijeme i da je to tko si bio u to vrijeme.

154
01:26:04,239 --> 01:26:09,119
[SPEAKER_01] A sada nešto događa sada, ovo je tko si ti sada.

155
01:26:09,439 --> 01:26:11,119
[SPEAKER_01] To bi se moglo promijeniti sutra.

156
01:26:11,359 --> 01:26:13,600
[SPEAKER_01] Tada ćeš biti onda ovo je tko si ti danas.

157
01:26:13,840 --> 01:26:17,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ne možeš biti tko si bio jučer tri tjedna.

158
01:26:18,159 --> 01:26:28,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ti si samo proizvod tko si bio u to vrijeme, a ti si samo proizvod tko si bio u to vrijeme.

159
01:26:31,680 --> 01:26:33,359
[SPEAKER_00] Imaš jednu posljednju pitanja za tebe.

160
01:26:33,520 --> 01:26:33,920
[SPEAKER_00] Oh, dobro.

161
01:26:34,880 --> 01:26:36,960
[SPEAKER_00] Prije nego što dođemo do pitanja publike.

162
01:28:30,000 --> 01:28:35,439
[SPEAKER_01] Kad shadow aspekti pokazuju, ne znamo da su to shadow aspekti jer su u subconsciousu.

163
01:28:35,520 --> 01:28:37,199
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, očito, nećete znati.

164
01:28:37,840 --> 01:28:41,359
[SPEAKER_01] The only way you know is koga upoznate na road.

165
01:28:42,239 --> 01:28:46,319
[SPEAKER_01] Do you have continual problems s jednom određenom tipom osobe?

166
01:28:46,640 --> 01:28:51,600
[SPEAKER_01] Do you have a repetitive pattern of situacije arising in your life that challenge you?

167
01:28:52,319 --> 01:28:55,199
[SPEAKER_01] Do you keep stumbling over the same blocks?

168
01:28:56,560 --> 01:29:02,560
[SPEAKER_01] These aspekti pokušavaju vam pokazati da su to vaša shadow, which is why I said earlier, just imagine a mirror.

169
01:29:03,680 --> 01:29:07,840
[SPEAKER_01] Because everything that happens to you is a reflection of who you believe yourself to be.

170
01:30:24,239 --> 01:30:31,119
